43
00:04:17,100 --> 00:04:18,970
So you mean...

44
00:04:19,050 --> 00:04:21,890
Gan Pu will betray the son of the late emperor?

45
00:04:27,970 --> 00:04:28,680
I...

46
00:04:29,400 --> 00:04:30,260
Gan Pu.

47
00:04:31,840 --> 00:04:33,560
I think when there's a problem,

48
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:36,360
it's better to just say it.

49
00:04:36,940 --> 00:04:39,270
I think it's the best way

50
00:04:39,270 --> 00:04:40,390
