51
00:04:41,510 --> 00:04:43,990
Hiding your thoughts

52
00:04:43,990 --> 00:04:46,190
will only make things worse.

53
00:04:47,450 --> 00:04:49,050
So what I want to say is

54
00:04:51,310 --> 00:04:52,690
