61
00:05:18,400 --> 00:05:19,180
We will not...

62
00:05:19,210 --> 00:05:20,290
We will never

63
00:05:20,310 --> 00:05:21,390
do those...

64
00:05:23,090 --> 00:05:24,710
those dirty things for our own interests.

65
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:38,770
But now,

66
00:05:39,290 --> 00:05:41,320
we have a common enemy:

67
00:05:41,550 --> 00:05:43,040
Mingyi Manor.

68
00:05:59,300 --> 00:06:00,730
Easier said

69
00:06:01,370 --> 00:06:03,970
than done.

70
00:06:07,190 --> 00:06:08,560
I also need to think carefully about it.

71
00:06:29,780 --> 00:06:31,090
I think

72
00:06:31,680 --> 00:06:33,360
something is wrong

73
00:06:33,580 --> 00:06:35,170
with their collaboration.

74
00:06:35,200 --> 00:06:36,390
Of course.

75
00:06:37,070 --> 00:06:38,880
Then why don't we just

76
00:06:38,900 --> 00:06:39,610
win Gan Pu over?

77
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:49,130
It's still not dawn yet?

78
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:50,770
All right, then.

79
00:06:51,440 --> 00:06:54,420
How come there was a tense situation?

80
00:06:54,580 --> 00:06:56,800
W-When was there a tense situation?

81
00:06:56,830 --> 00:06:58,210
You need to

82
00:06:58,659 --> 00:07:01,500
