I don't see any.

122
00:11:03,140 --> 00:11:04,190
Are you stupid?

123
00:11:04,690 --> 00:11:06,540
How can you see them at night?

124
00:11:06,880 --> 00:11:08,570
Try again during the daytime tomorrow.

125
00:11:09,530 --> 00:11:11,320
I can see them tomorrow morning.

126
00:11:13,430 --> 00:11:15,390
You really are stupid.

127
00:11:15,760 --> 00:11:17,320
How can you see them during the daytime?

128
00:11:17,470 --> 00:11:18,930
At night,

129
00:11:19,160 --> 00:11:23,230
the mosquitos' bodies will be carried away by ants.

130
00:11:40,630 --> 00:11:41,790
What is Qing Cai doing?

131
00:11:42,410 --> 00:11:43,440
He's making a swing.

132
00:11:44,320 --> 00:11:46,060
Why does he suddenly want to make that?

133
00:11:47,160 --> 00:11:48,080
Gan Pu.

134
00:11:51,760 --> 00:11:53,100
That was close today.

135
00:11:53,630 --> 00:11:55,140
I almost made a huge mistake.

136
00:11:59,300 --> 00:12:00,700
It happened so suddenly.

137
00:12:02,220 --> 00:12:04,040
I was thoughtless.

138
00:12:04,520 --> 00:12:06,310
I'm reluctant to fight against you.

139
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:08,780
I owe you two lives.

140
00:12:09,790 --> 00:12:10,910
That doesn't count.

141
00:12:11,300 --> 00:12:12,940
As a doctor, it's my duty to save people.

142
00:12:13,570 --> 00:12:15,180
To you, it's your duty.

143
00:12:15,290 --> 00:12:17,570
But to me, it's a favor.

144
00:12:18,080 --> 00:12:20,290
If you need to fight against me one day,

145
00:12:20,320 --> 00:12:21,250
no need to show mercy.

146
00:12:22,190 --> 00:12:23,060
I owe you.

147
00:12:25,590 --> 00:12:27,110
You can't die yet.

148
00:12:28,370 --> 00:12:30,750
Your life isn't yours either.

149
00:12:35,340 --> 00:12:36,600
So,

150
00:12:36,930 --> 00:12:38,780
when you should fight against me,

151
00:12:39,300 --> 00:12:40,680
you don't need to show mercy either.

152
00:12:44,210 --> 00:12:46,880
How come... you know everything?

153
00:12:47,910 --> 00:12:48,850
Not really.

154
00:12:49,340 --> 00:12:52,070
I found out through investigations.

155
00:12:53,670 --> 00:12:55,370
I'm very curious.

156
00:12:55,390 --> 00:12:57,470
How did you manage to follow Qing Cai?

157
00:12:57,730 --> 00:12:59,310
You weren't there.

158
00:12:59,710 --> 00:13:01,440
And you don't know martial arts,

159
00:13:01,460 --> 00:13:03,060
let alone the speed for it.

160
00:13:06,070 --> 00:13:08,010
Mingyi Manor's Soul-tracking Incense

161
00:13:08,520 --> 00:13:11,640
is like a child's toy to me.

162
00:13:12,730 --> 00:13:13,780
I see.

163
00:13:14,710 --> 00:13:18,030
But why did you only investigate

164
00:13:18,380 --> 00:13:19,310
and never make a move?

165
00:13:25,810 --> 00:13:27,110
We are pawns.

166
00:13:28,420 --> 00:13:30,110
We just need to do what a pawn should do.

167
00:13:31,110 --> 00:13:33,070
As a pawn,

168
00:13:33,450 --> 00:13:34,790
