182
00:14:08,880 --> 00:14:10,750
I went beyond my role

183
00:14:11,630 --> 00:14:12,960
and disrupted the game.

184
00:14:15,410 --> 00:14:17,470
So you're telling me this

185
00:14:17,580 --> 00:14:19,030
