187
00:14:21,800 --> 00:14:22,680
Yes.

188
00:14:23,110 --> 00:14:25,100
It's just irrelevant information.

189
00:14:25,590 --> 00:14:26,360
But

190
00:14:27,110 --> 00:14:28,320
this will

191
00:14:28,900 --> 00:14:32,670
