193
00:14:38,420 --> 00:14:39,800
You mean emotionally?

194
00:14:41,560 --> 00:14:43,150
You already gave up.

195
00:14:43,860 --> 00:14:45,200
Why can't I?

196
00:14:46,110 --> 00:14:46,640
I...

197
00:14:46,660 --> 00:14:49,030
